reviewText:
Thoroughly delightful, illustrative and insightful walk with a Master of so many disciplines, cultures, ages and languages.

Miss him dearly!
A fabulous resource from teacher Ken-for students and teachers of Shamanism!

HH2W  Ken Harsh has done it again.  Another fantastic lecture to savor over and over again.  I would highly recommend any of Ken's lectures on DVD to anyone on the path.  Thank you for sharing your knowledge.
